Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.74,0:23:52.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.65,0:00:05.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為連日的高溫天氣　這裡大洗海水浴場
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.23,0:00:07.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聚集了很多客人十分熱鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.40,0:00:12.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小時候　我還以為大洗海水浴場是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.91,0:00:15.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大笑海水浴場
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.67,0:00:18.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然還是很奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.75,0:00:21.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪的是你的腦袋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.38,0:00:24.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼說的話今年還沒去過海邊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.66,0:00:30.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出生以來就沒去過海邊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.70,0:00:33.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒去過海邊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.77,0:00:35.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,農嘟嘟　這是真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.06,0:00:39.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的一次也沒見過海嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.77,0:00:42.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為岐阜縣沒有海啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.92,0:00:44.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修學旅行之類的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.91,0:00:48.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小學的修學旅行去的是京都和奈良
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.69,0:00:51.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中學的修學旅行也是京都奈良
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.92,0:00:55.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這鐵定是地域陰謀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.12,0:00:56.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.81,0:00:58.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去海邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.48,0:01:01.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果調整大家的時間的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.18,0:01:03.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總會有一天用空的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.01,0:01:06.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對啊　這次的假期大家一起去海邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.15,0:01:08.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.21,0:01:10.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,林檎穿泳裝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.49,0:01:13.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,林檎穿泳裝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.37,0:01:15.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,林檎穿泳裝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.80,0:01:17.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的確不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.55,0:01:19.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許還能留下美好回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.06,0:01:20.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.32,0:01:23.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難得的假期　去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.47,0:01:24.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.59,0:01:27.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是　到了那天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.90,0:01:31.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常強勢的颱風9號
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.01,0:01:32.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保持著強勁的勢頭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.73,0:01:34.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從東海地區登陸了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.63,0:01:37.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,颱風來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.48,0:03:21.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.48,0:03:15.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美濃田茂市全市有大雨洪水暴風雷電落石警報
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.84,0:03:18.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滿貫1萬2千點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.38,0:03:20.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警報的滿漢全席啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.33,0:03:22.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是這裡再加上潮水海浪警報的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.90,0:03:26.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就直接跳滿1萬8千點了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.01,0:03:27.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們這沒有海
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.56,0:03:29.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,颱風也就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.27,0:03:30.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一到傍晚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.50,0:03:32.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都是不定時暴雨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.00,0:03:34.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這附近的夏天真是鬧騰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.24,0:03:36.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去海邊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.01,0:03:37.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去海邊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.38,0:03:40.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去海邊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.35,0:03:42.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有更鬧騰的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.44,0:03:44.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正都要濕的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.45,0:03:47.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下雨也沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.02,0:03:48.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.73,0:03:50.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去海邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.62,0:03:52.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別瞎說了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.11,0:03:53.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,電車和大巴都停了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.70,0:03:54.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒法去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.82,0:03:56.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就騎自行車去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.60,0:03:58.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那更不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.34,0:04:00.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連自行車都會被吹走的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.39,0:04:02.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了　放棄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.49,0:04:05.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次你想去哪我都帶你去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.83,0:04:07.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就先忍忍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.14,0:04:08.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪都行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.05,0:04:09.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯　哪兒都行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.49,0:04:10.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有想去的地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.86,0:04:12.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯　那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.67,0:04:14.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.12,0:04:15.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要陷落了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.30,0:04:17.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在強大的力量下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.03,0:04:19.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你　你是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.24,0:04:21.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Money　金上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.06,0:04:22.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.02,0:04:24.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為有實習就過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.34,0:04:27.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為颱風誰都沒來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.83,0:04:29.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大巴和電車也沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.88,0:04:33.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,道路積水了老師好像也中途回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.10,0:04:35.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼　沒有實習了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.74,0:04:37.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不僅如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.80,0:04:40.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒法走了我都沒法回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.81,0:04:41.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.55,0:04:43.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暫時讓我呆在這吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.17,0:04:44.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.16,0:04:45.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常情況嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.27,0:04:47.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Money　什麼實習啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.59,0:04:49.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cymbidium的移栽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.52,0:04:51.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cymbi　向上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.77,0:04:54.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cymbidium　是蘭花的一種
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.22,0:04:56.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盛開在東南亞高地的一種花
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.86,0:04:58.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡乾燥涼爽的氣候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.97,0:05:01.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以夏天如果不移到山上去上會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.99,0:05:03.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就會飛花
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.87,0:05:05.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飛花　是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.88,0:05:08.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太熱的話就會生長異常
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.28,0:05:10.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話就沒有價值了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.47,0:05:12.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好詳細啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.63,0:05:13.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜歡花嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.32,0:05:15.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花可是會變成錢嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.16,0:05:16.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一語中的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.27,0:05:20.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很久以前賣到過上十甚至上百萬日元
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.07,0:05:22.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,壓倒性　壓倒性的高價花
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.98,0:05:28.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的實習本來是用小客車把Cymbi運上去的
