Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.96,0:09:01.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼那麼吵　你們幾個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.07,0:09:02.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嚇到牛了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.74,0:09:04.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　良田同學
