Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.93,0:18:45.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.50,0:18:47.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為拖拉機啊收割機什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.84,0:18:49.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都沒有雨刷啥的啊
